Subject: BurleXercise: A Burlesque Inspired Dance Fitness
Description: BurleXercise is a fitness class created by Deborah O'Connell that takes the 'follow the leader' format that other fitness classes frequently use and puts burlesque inspired movement to it. This is not a burlesque how-to, this is a fitness class inspired by burlesque.  Speakers include:Deborah O'Connell - Track: Life  - Duration: 1 hour
